episodes.title: Inside Canada’s STRANGEST Cult
episodes.description: Who is Romana Didulo, the self-proclaimed “Queen of Canada? She leads one of the strangest cult movements in modern Canadian history. Claiming the throne of a nation that doesn’t recognize her, she’s built a decently large following online by spreading conspiracy theories, making outrageous proclamations, and presenting herself as Canada’s rightful ruler. But behind the spectacle is a darker truth: vulnerable people being manipulated, families torn apart, and entire communities left to deal with the chaos she leaves behind. In this video, we uncover the origins of the fake“Queen of Canada” — how she rose from obscurity to cult figure, the tactics she uses to secure loyalty, and how her movement feeds on misinformation, fear, and false hope.
